11324_geroscience_sidebar_icons2_telomere-attrition.jpg?resize=450%2C450&amp;ssl=1 450w, https://i0.wp.com/www.sciencenews.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/011324_geroscience_sidebar_icons2_telomere-attrition.jpg?resize=186%2C186&amp;ssl=1 186w, https://i0.wp.com/www.sciencenews.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/011324_geroscience_sidebar_icons2_telomere-attrition.jpg?resize=580%2C580&amp;ssl=1 580w, https://i0.wp.com/www.sciencenews.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/011324_geroscience_sidebar_icons2_telomere-attrition.jpg?resize=214%2C214&amp;ssl=1 214w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></figure></div></div><div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow" style="flex-basis:80%;text-align:right;direction:rtl"><p style=";text-align:right;direction:rtl"> <strong>שחיקה של טלומרים</strong> היא הנזק המצטבר או אובדן ה-DNA בקצוות הכרומוזומים, הנקראים טלומרים. </p></div></div><div class="wp-block-columns is-not-stacked-on-mobile is-layout-flex wp-container-9" style=";text-align:right;direction:rtl"><div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow" style="flex-basis:20%;text-align:right;direction:rtl"><div class="wp-block-image is-style-default has-aligncenter" style=";text-align:right;direction:rtl"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="450" height="450" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.sciencenews.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/011324_geroscience_sidebar_icons3_epigenetic-alterations.jpg?resize=450%2C450&#038;ssl=1" alt="סמל מתילציה" class="wp-image-3134773" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/www.sciencenews.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/011324_geroscience_sidebar_icons3_epigenetic-alterations.jpg?resize=450%2C450&amp;ssl=1 450w, https://i0.wp.com/www.sciencenews.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/011324_geroscience_sidebar_icons3_epigenetic-alterations.jpg?resize=383%2C383&amp;ssl=1 383w, https://i0.wp.com/www.sciencenews.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/011324_geroscience_sidebar_icons3_epigenetic-alterations.jpg?resize=186%2C186&amp;s